maneuvers.narrative: Start out going southwest on Reservoir St/MA-31 toward Pleasant St. Continue to follow MA-31.
Turn left onto Grove St/MA-31.
Turn right onto Maple St/MA-31.
Turn left onto Richards Ave/MA-31/MA-56.
Turn slight right onto Church St/MA-31.
Turn slight right onto West St/MA-31. Continue to follow MA-31.
Turn right onto Meadow Rd.
Meadow Rd becomes W Main St.
Turn right onto W Main St/MA-9.
Turn left onto Podunk Pike/MA-49. Continue to follow MA-49.
Turn right onto Charlton Rd/US-20 W. Continue to follow US-20 W.
Merge onto I-84 W via the ramp on the left toward Hartford CT (Passing through Connecticut and New York, then crossing into Pennsylvania).
Merge onto I-81 S via the exit on the left toward Wilkes-Barre.
Merge onto I-80 W via EXIT 151B toward Bloomsburg (Portions toll) (Passing through Ohio, then crossing into Indiana).
Merge onto I-80 W/I-94 W via EXIT 21 toward IN-51 S (Crossing into Illinois).
Keep left to take I-80 W/I-294 N toward Wisconsin-Iowa (Portions toll).
Take the I-80 W exit toward Iowa.
Merge onto I-80 W (Portions toll).
Stay straight to go onto I-280 W (Crossing into Iowa).
Merge onto I-80 W via the exit on the left toward Des Moines (Crossing into Nebraska).
Merge onto I-76 W via EXIT 102 on the left toward Denver (Crossing into Colorado).
I-76 W becomes I-70 W (Crossing into Utah).
Merge onto I-15 S via the exit on the left toward Las Vegas (Passing through Arizona and Nevada, then crossing into California).
Merge onto I-215 S via EXIT 123 toward San Bernadino/Riverside.
Merge onto I-15 S.
Merge onto I-10 W via EXIT 109A toward Los Angeles.
Take San Bernardino Fwy toward US-101/Los Angeles.
San Bernardino Fwy becomes US-101 N.
Take the Spring St exit, EXIT 2C.
Turn right onto N Spring St.
Turn left onto W 1st St.
Welcome to LOS ANGELES, CA.
